If you set emulator to `true` or `false` above, you'll be able to rewrite such tests as:

  if $emulator; then
     # Emulator is used.
     # ...
  fi

For negative conditions, you can use:

  if $emulator; then :; else
    # Emulator is not used.
    # ...
  fi

